descriptions:
Product Name: Electronic Organizer Travel USB Cable Accessories Bag/Case

Description:

This Electronic Organizer is the perfect solution to keep all your electronic accessories neatly organized and easily accessible while traveling, for family use, or any other situation where you need to carry multiple electronic items.

Material and Dimensions:
Constructed from Waterproof, Shockproof, Heavy-duty, and Durable Material, this organizer ensures your items are safe and secure. Its external dimensions are 7.48 inches (length), 4.33 inches (width), and 2.16 inches (height).

Compartments and Storage Capacity:
This bag/case features 2 compartments, providing ample space to store a variety of items such as a power bank, external hard drive, SD memory card, cables, earphone, connector adapter, stationeries (pen, pencil, highlighter, gel pen, eraser), digital camera, selfie stick, basic first aid items, makeup, passport, and smartphones.

Portability:
The organizer comes with a portable belt for easy carrying, and it can also be hand-carried or slipped into a backpack. Its compact size makes it ideal for travel or family use.

Multi-Use:
Apart from being an electronic organizer, this bag/case can also serve as a Cosmetic Carrying Bag, adding to its versatility.

Warranty:
We offer a replacement or refund if you are dissatisfied with the product or if it has any defects.

Package Contents:
1 Pcs Electronics Organizer
